{"tid":433113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【恐怖18秒】油門當腳掣？ 女司機失控狂撞途人","createTime":"2017-10-12T06:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T09:57:17.000Z","uid":49391,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7046d7449d7d28ef7c8189ed030b17655d540198","tid":433113,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:08:41.000Z","msg":"天津發生恐怖車禍，一名女司機疑誤將油門當腳掣，失控狂撞途人。<br />\n<br />\n今日早上11時許，濱海新區漢沽一屋苑門口外，原本停泊一輛紅色私家車。該紅色私家車突然開動，失控衝上行人路，途人見狀紛紛走避，惟仍有有多名途人被撞倒。車輛未有即時煞停，在路上兜了兩個圈，18秒後才停車。據警方通報，肇事者為一名女性，事故原因為其駕駛時操作不當，目前已被公安機關控制。<br />\n秒拍 <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171011/57319040\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171011%2F57319040&d=x7MGXgOW72Kzxyel2SOqzJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=00075c87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20171011%2F57319040&h=583a29f9\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20171011/57319040</a>"},{"pid":"77ba2393e328d5cc83e9170d77720a6dacbce42e","tid":433113,"uid":130143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:15:16.000Z","msg":"18 秒reaction time<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過咁耐先識得放開油門"},{"pid":"60547f5100abdaf4f7034c41ef95ec89aca8d760","tid":433113,"uid":51978,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:19:09.000Z","msg":"應該打靶<br />\n<br />\n雖然係無心<br />\n<br />\n不過弱智到恁 不宜久待人世"},{"pid":"a9734308bf71553de4c6754dfc1bcb436488df8d","tid":433113,"uid":36995,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"兩圈後個泊位好準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69de904dbb09194209a0d8ec6f09bcc39a33f793","tid":433113,"uid":26093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-12T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"女人揸車，見到都驚"},{"pid":"9ebf6cc0f5f2b7258eb6de5f4539eb2f